                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ:<gap reason="omitted"/>እጽሕፍ: ማኅሌተ: ጽጌ: በስመ: እግዚአብሔር: ሥሉስ: በልሳነ: ኵሉ: ፍጡር: ወበስምኪ: ማርያም: መራሂተ: ኃጥዕ: ዕውር:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                   </msItem>
                     	<msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="48r" to="49r" facs="050">Fols 48r–49r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2300Sebhat">Sǝbḥata fǝqur</title>
                      <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰአል፡ ሚካኤል፡ አስተምር፡ ለነ፡…</incipit>
                      <note>continued from the end of <locus target="#90r" facs="092">fol. 90r</locus></note>
                    </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="50r" to="75r" facs="052">Fols 50r–75r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas">Wǝddāse
                                                  Māryām</title>
                      <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">እግዝእትየ: ፍትሕኒ: እማዕሰሩ: ለሰይጣን: እሙ: ለመድኅን: ወለተ: ብርሃን። ፈቀደ: እግዚእ: ያግዕዞ: ለአዳም:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                    </msItem>
                      	<msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="75r" to="85r" facs="077">Fols 75r–85r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1113Anqasa">ʾAnqaṣa
                                                  bǝrhān</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                      </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="85r" to="85r" facs="087">Fols 85r–85r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3108RepCh388">Yǝweddǝsǝwwa
                                                  malāʾǝkt la-Māryām</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                      </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="85v" to="90r" facs="088">Fols 85v–90r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2300Sebhat">Sǝbḥata fǝqur</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">መልአከ: ምክሩ: ለቃል: ሚካኤል: ፫ጊዜ: ሰአል: ለነ: ሚካኤል: ፫ጊዜ: አስተምህር: ለነ: ገብ(ር)ኤል: ሚካኤ(ል): መጋቢ: ለነፍሰ: ኵሉ: ፍጥረት:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                      </msItem>
